<font class="righthead">CEA Technology and Standards</font>
<br>
The CEA Technology & Standards mission is to grow the consumer electronics industry through technical support. T&S are a vital connection between consumers, retailers and manufacturers of consumer electronics, providing project management and a forum for industry to develop standards and technical publications.
